      "id": "sybil_4_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presented is an investment-grade E46 M3, a pinnacle of atmospheric induction. At its heart lies the S54B32 straight-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing, both meticulously maintained for peak volumetric efficiency. Power is routed through a precise Getrag six-speed manual gearbox to a variable M-differential lock. The chassis integrity is flawless, with documented subframe reinforcement and factory-spec bushings ensuring razor-sharp kinematics. This specimen retains its original mechanical luster, exhibiting no thermal degradation or fluid seepage. Every component, from the high-pressure VANOS lines to the multi-link rear suspension, operates in perfect synchronicity, offering a raw, unadulterated driving experience that defines the golden era of the M-division.",
